 italic;">Make It New</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. London: Faber and Faber.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Price, Huw. 1997 [1996].</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;"> Time’s Arrow and Archimedes’ Point: New Directions for the Physics of Time.</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;"> Oxford: Oxford University Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Ralston, W</span><a name="_Hlt359533434"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">.</span></a><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">R.S. 1872. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The Songs of the Russian People: as illustrative of Slavonic mythology and </span><a name="_Hlt359533488"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">R</span></a><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">ussian social life</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. London: Ellis &amp; Green, 1872.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Ritsos, Yiannis. 1966. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Romiosýne</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">.</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;"> </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Athens: Themelio. </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. Undated. ‘</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Ο Γιάννης Ρίτσος στην αραβική γλώσσα - Η “Ρωμιοσύνη”’ [</span><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nXX5X7o4kdc"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">‘Ritsos in t</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">h</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">e Arabic Language – “Romiosyne”</span></a><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">’]. A recording of Ritsos reading part of the poem in Greek, including the lines mentioned in this interview. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">YouTube</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Saussure, Ferdinand de. 1971 [1915]. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Cours de linguistique générale</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">.  Paris: Payot.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Seferis, George. 1960. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Poems</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Tr. Rex Warner. London: The Bodley Head.</span></p><p